2. What is AWS
==================
-- Enables on-demand service like compute, storage, networking, etc.

3. AWS Career
--------------
-- Cloud Architect
---- Designs the Architect of the cloud. Blue Prints Designs
---- Understand Cloud Services
---- Design Multi Tier Cloud Application
---- Implement Cost Control Strategies

-- Cloud Developer
---- Develop the blue prints into the cloud application
---- Expertise in Programming Language
---- Engage in DevOps Practice
---- Understand SDLC

-- Cloud Adminstrator
---- Maintenance cloud
---- Understand System Opertation & VM
---- Ability to Migrate & Monitor on-premise Data

