7. AWS Elastic Load Balancer
----------------------------
-- Distribute the load among the instences interms of the incoming traffics.
-- Types of Load Balance
----- Classic Load Balance
----- Network Load Balance
----- Application Load Balance

8. AWS Autoscaling
------------------
-- EC2 instances will always be available for upscale and downscale according to the load or traffic.

9. AWS EC2 (Basic Level)
------------------------
-- Instances
-- Types of Instances
